N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 163.6 - Trademark program participation fee

State Regulations

The fee for participation in this program shall not exceed
the estimated costs of the services provided. Such costs shall include the
following: program administration; inspection expenses such as personal
services, travel, equipment, supplies and materials; and other expenses
incidental to carrying out the trademark program. The participation fee shall
be charged on a product basis as follows: Product
